{"tid":1418203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地必須對準政權！！革命、放核彈、通通我地都唔會割，但係我地要對準政權黎放！！！文宣入黎！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:35:50.000Z","uid":110109,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2807f29689a45caf5d5929997e0da8cd220da6","tid":1418203,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢篇講文宣既</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日一日喺黃大仙<br />\n我真係好心痛 睇到<br />\n我地既年輕既抗爭者到老年既街坊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">奮 不 顧 身</span></span><br />\n去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗爭</span></span><br />\n去凸顯政府既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不公</span></span><br />\n去凸顯政府既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">失信</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港警察<br />\n繼續比人當槍使<br />\n已經睇到一步步接近金屬疲勞，甚至即將失控。<br />\n<br />\n物理定律，作用同反作用力<br />\n我地其實一樣喺一次次抗爭中，慢慢身心俱疲、肉體精神都繃得極緊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天琦講過<br />\n我地要用智慧、警覺凌駕仇恨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港即將黎到命運既交叉點<br />\n今日一役 我地睇到我地勇武派既極強堅韌既精神<br />\n</span></span><br />\n下一步我地更需要趕上既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係更強大既文宣<br />\n<br />\n我地要比敵人更冷靜、<br />\n更文武兼備<br />\n我地係帶黎希望既正義之師</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因此必須全力<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對準政權<br />\n逼迫建制<br />\n怠警軍心<br />\n智慧凌駕仇恨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d4d673c54da98ef6d64542b1829ca2ef2a22b38","tid":1418203,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"對準政權、一次比一次強大！"},{"pid":"67b158c21468d207161e770d39994f89b044a4dd","tid":1418203,"u